---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Bravura Builders — Luxury Remodels & Design-Build in Metro Atlanta"
  description="Bravura Builders runs high-end remodels, commercial renovations, and in-house design across the Atlanta metro. Fixed line-item proposals and free construction estimates."
>
  <section class="hero-dark on-dark" aria-label="Introduction">
    <div class="grid-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="glow g1" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="glow g2" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <svg class="roofline" viewBox="0 0 900 340" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M30,320 V160 L250,42 L470,160 V320"></path>
      <path class="warm" d="M470,160 H880 M250,42 L320,80 M320,80 V38 H352 V98"></path>
      <path d="M180,200 h70 v58 h-70 z M215,200 v58 M180,229 h70"></path>
    </svg>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow hero-load"
            >Luxury remodels &middot; Commercial &middot; Design-build &middot; Atlanta metro</span
          >
          <h1>
            <span class="line"><span>Technical Skill,</span></span>
            <span class="line"><span><em>Brilliant Design,</em></span></span>
            <span class="line"><span>Flawless Results.</span></span>
          </h1>
          <p class="hero-sub hero-load d1">
            Bravura Builders runs high-end remodels and commercial renovations with big-city
            scheduling rigor, priced with the transparency of a fixed, line-item proposal.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-ctas hero-load d2">
            <a class="btn" href="/contact">Get a free estimate <span class="arr">&rarr;</span></a>
            <a class="btn ghost" href="/design">Start with design</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="definition hero-load d3">
          <span class="word">bra&middot;vu&middot;ra</span><span class="phon"
            >/br&#601;&rsquo;v(y)o&#828;or&#601;/</span
          ><span class="pos">noun</span>
          <p>
            &ldquo;Great technical skill and <u>brilliance</u> shown in a performance or activity.&rdquo;
          </p>
          <p class="tagline">Bring bravura to your next remodel.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="stat hero-load d2">
          <div class="num"><span data-count="4">0</span> <small>YEARS</small></div><div class="lbl">
            Senior Project Management, Manhattan Construction
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat hero-load d2">
          <div class="num"><span data-count="120">0</span><small>+</small></div><div class="lbl">
            Units renovated, NYC &amp; Atlanta
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat hero-load d3">
          <div class="num"><span data-count="150000">0</span> <small>FT.&sup2;</small></div><div
            class="lbl"
          >
            Delivered across residential &amp; commercial
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="marquee" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="track">
        <div class="set">
          <span>Luxury remodels</span><i class="dia"></i>
          <span>Commercial renovation</span><i class="dia"></i>
          <span>Ground-up construction</span><i class="dia"></i>
          <span>In-house design</span><i class="dia"></i>
          <span>Atlanta metro</span><i class="dia"></i>
          <span>Licensed &amp; insured</span><i class="dia"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="set">
          <span>Luxury remodels</span><i class="dia"></i>
          <span>Commercial renovation</span><i class="dia"></i>
          <span>Ground-up construction</span><i class="dia"></i>
          <span>In-house design</span><i class="dia"></i>
          <span>Atlanta metro</span><i class="dia"></i>
          <span>Licensed &amp; insured</span><i class="dia"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="doors-head rv">
        <span class="eyebrow">Two ways to start</span>
        <h2>Build with us. Or design with us first.</h2>
        <p>Construction and in-house design are separate doors. Walk through either one.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="doors stagger">
        <div class="door construction rv">
          <span class="badge">Free estimates</span>
          <h3>Construction</h3>
          <p>Full-service general contracting, priced line by line before work begins.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Luxury high-end residential remodels</li>
            <li>Commercial renovations &amp; build-outs</li>
            <li>Ground-up construction</li>
            <li>Pre-construction &amp; estimating</li>
          </ul>
          <a class="btn blue" href="/construction"
            >Explore construction <span class="arr">&rarr;</span></a
          >
        </div>
        <div class="door design rv">
          <span class="badge">Paid service &middot; A to Z</span>
          <h3>In-House Design</h3>
          <p>A complete design package, from first concept to construction-ready documents.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Full design from concept to construction docs</li>
            <li>3D renderings &amp; style boards</li>
            <li>Plans &amp; specifications</li>
            <li>Standalone: take your designs anywhere</li>
          </ul>
          <a class="btn" href="/design">Explore design <span class="arr">&rarr;</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="price-note rv">
        <span class="i" aria-hidden="true">$</span>
        <span
          ><b>Clear pricing, no blending:</b> a construction estimate is always free. Design is a paid
          engagement, even if you don&rsquo;t build with Bravura, and the drawings are yours to keep.</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="featured">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="sec-head rv">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">Featured projects</span>
          <h2>Finished work, photographed as built.</h2>
        </div>
        <a class="btn ghost" href="/projects">See all projects <span class="arr">&rarr;</span></a>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-grid stagger">
        <a class="card big rv" href="/projects"
          ><img
            src="/img/projects/DSC07647.jpg"
            alt="Kitchen remodel with walnut cabinetry, white uppers, and a black stone waterfall island"
            loading="lazy"
          /><div class="cap"><b>Walnut &amp; stone kitchen</b><span>Full gut remodel</span></div></a
        >
        <a class="card sm rv" href="/projects"
          ><img
            src="/img/projects/DSC08124.jpg"
            alt="Bathroom in black herringbone tile with glass shower"
            loading="lazy"
          /><div class="cap"><b>Herringbone bath</b><span>Bath renovation</span></div></a
        >
        <a class="card sm rv" href="/projects"
          ><img
            src="/img/projects/DSC07609.jpg"
            alt="Parlor floor with exposed brick fireplace and new oak floors"
            loading="lazy"
          /><div class="cap"><b>Parlor floor restoration</b><span>Full floor</span></div></a
        >
        <a class="card w1 rv" href="/projects"
          ><img
            src="/img/projects/IMG_2920.jpg"
            alt="Kitchen remodel with rift-oak cabinets and matte black appliances"
            loading="lazy"
          /><div class="cap">
            <b>Rift oak &amp; brass kitchen</b><span>Kitchen remodel</span>
          </div></a
        >
        <a class="card w2 rv" href="/projects"
          ><img
            src="/img/projects/DSC07404.jpg"
            alt="Kitchen renovation with two-tone cabinetry and marble counters"
            loading="lazy"
          /><div class="cap"><b>Two-tone kitchen</b><span>Full gut remodel</span></div></a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="quotes on-dark">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="sec-head rv">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">Client reviews</span>
          <h2>What clients say.</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="quote-grid stagger">
        <div class="quote rv">
          <span class="stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars"
            >&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span
          ><p>
            Had a great experience working with Bravura! Highly recommend using them for a
            professional and easy experience.
          </p><span class="who">Ariel &middot; Google review</span>
        </div>
        <div class="quote rv">
          <span class="stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars"
            >&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span
          ><p>Had an amazing experience with Bravura Builders. Highly recommend!!</p><span
            class="who">Abe &middot; Google review</span
          >
        </div>
        <a
          class="quote review-cta rv"
          href="https://g.page/r/CdMEQkwy6YO9EAI/review"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          ><span class="stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars"
            >&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span
          ><span class="g">5.0<b>on Google</b></span><p>
            Real five-star reviews from Bravura clients. Read them all, or add your own.
          </p><span class="who">See all reviews <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></span></a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="cta-box rv">
        <div>
          <h2>Tell us what you&rsquo;re building.</h2>
          <p>
            A free, no-obligation estimate for construction, or a design engagement that starts with
            a conversation.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="actions">
          <a class="btn blue" href="/contact">Get a free estimate <span class="arr">&rarr;</span></a
          >
          <a class="btn ghost" href="/contact">Start with design</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
